17 SECTION 1. AMENDATORY Section 10, Chapter 303, O.S.L.
18 2024 (36 O.S. Supp. 2024, Section 6570.9), is amended to read as
19 follows:
20 Section 6570.9. A. If a prior authorization is required for a
21 health care service, other than for inpatient care, for the
22 treatment of a chronic condition of an enrollee, then the prior
23 authorization shall remain valid for at least six (6) months from
24 the date the health care provider receives the prior authorization
